          "user_thumbnail": "https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/a-/ALV-UjUN-lVHPjlmxEy9O37icCazoC-DWmTduW-7gggQ5tsG4E-zmMMt=s120-c-rp-mo-ba12-br100",
          "description": "They used to be much more helpful and friendlier. Nowadays? That\u2019s a complete joke. Customer service sucks and so lackadaisical, you\u2019re being treated as an inconvenience. Also, they\u2019ll never notify me when the medication script has been sent over - I always have to chase them up. It\u2019s been downhill from there ever since they royally screwed up on my medication once early last year. Recently, they sent me a text with someone else\u2019s name regarding their medication delivery. Careless mistakes with unfriendly and unhelpful service to boot - a winning combo.",
          "link": "https://www.google.com/maps/reviews/data=!4m8!14m7!1m6!2m5!1sCi9DQUlRQUNvZENodHljRjlvT2pWQlNWOXJkRXMzVGxwRmRsSnFNMU5LVVhnMWRtYxAB!2m1!1s0x0:0x73f4f995c6d87563!3m1!1s2@1:CAIQACodChtycF9oOjVBSV9rdEs3TlpFdlJqM1NKUXg1dmc%7C%7C?hl=en",
