          "description": "Meds pharmacy has been amazing so far! Ever since I switched over, they have been on top of their game and provided with really good service. Deliveries come straight to my house, and sometimes to my office if I need to switch. I also downloaded their app and get notifications when my script is ready. They are truly a full service pharmacy. Highly Recommend!\n\nUpdate! Meds Pharmacy recently released a Travel Kit with all the most important medications and wow its a lifesaver. There is a medication for almost every possible scenario. I travel alot, and to different countries, so now this kit comes with me everywhere! Yes, you would need your doctor to prescribe it for you but it's so worth it!  Ask the Pharmacy how to get one.",
